<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
ALO- Assistance for Landless Organization is a Non-Profit dedicated to empowering the Landless and disadvantaged communities in Bangladesh...
</p>

<a href="/about" class="text-green-700 font-semibold">
Read More →
